Package org.neo4j.kernel.impl.util.diffsets

Class RemovalsCountingDiffSets

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.neo4j.kernel.impl.util.diffsets.MutableLongDiffSetsImpl
      • org.neo4j.kernel.impl.util.diffsets.RemovalsCountingDiffSets
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MutableLongDiffSets, LongDiffSets
    public class RemovalsCountingDiffSets
extends MutableLongDiffSetsImpl
    This class works around the fact that create-delete in the same transaction is a no-op in MutableDiffSetsImpl, whereas we need to know total number of explicit removals.
